/**
 * ai-service.ts
 * AI Enhancement Layer for CareerForge.
 *
 * ARCHITECTURE:
 * This service ONLY enhances already-extracted data.
 * It is NOT responsible for extracting data from resumes.
 * The rule-based parser (resume-parser.ts) handles extraction.
 *
 * FAILOVER CHAIN:
 * Primary free model → Backup free model → Local programmatic enhancement
 * The user is NEVER blocked if all AI calls fail.
 */

